title: Best of Christian Hip-Hop Vol. 1 Mixtape
description:
This is Best of Christian Hip-Hop Vol. 1 Mixtape. I had originally planned on releasing this in January, but due to lack of interest, I postponed it. I am releasing it now with hopes of renewed interest. I intend to release 7 volumes. If you like the release please vote for the tracks you would like to see on vol. 2. You can do that by posting a comment on pirate bay or feed them the word facebook page. Thank You and enjoy.

All songs are 2010 or earlier requests for future volumes should follow this criteria. If I am still around in 2020 I will do 7 volumes of 2011-2020, you can save those requests for then.
